      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2021 R2) is commercially validated and operates under a documented software quality assurance plan compliant with FDA software guidance. Version control, regression testing, and release documentation are maintained. Achieved level 2 meets the required level 2 for this MRL."
