      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including lid-driven cavity and pipe flow were executed to verify solver implementation. Results matched published reference solutions within acceptable tolerances. Code verification is consistent with MRL 2 requirements."
