    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out as not required at MRL 2 for a Class II device. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended use of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB conditions. The model is accepted for the stated context of use.",
